text: Chkalovskoye () is a rural locality (a village) in Kaltovsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 134 as of 2010. There are three streets. == Geography == It is located 30 km from Iglino, 7 km from Kaltovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Chkalovskoye, Republic of Bashkortostan
